    <entry>
      <title>kick start 2020 round A第四题</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/25/kick-start-2020-round-A%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E9%A2%98/"/>
      <url>/2020/03/25/kick-start-2020-round-A%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E9%A2%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="题目大意"><a href="#题目大意" class="headerlink" title="题目大意"></a>题目大意</h2><p>给定$N$个字符串，和数字$K$，并保证$K|N$，那么可以将这$N$个字符串分成$N/K$组，每组$K$个，每一组内的分数定义为这一组字符串的最长公共前缀长度。求使得分数总和最大的分组的分数和。</p><h2 id="题目分析"><a href="#题目分析" class="headerlink" title="题目分析"></a>题目分析</h2><p>先说结论：题目等价于对每一个可能的前缀，包含该前缀的字符串数量求和记为$S_i$，求出$\sum_i{\lfloor S_i / K \rfloor}$，即为最终答案。考虑每一种分组方案的分数，如果某一组最长前缀为长度为$r$，那么相当于这个前缀的每一个前缀都贡献了1，总的贡献除以$K$就是分数$r$。而一个前缀如果在所有字符串中出现了$S$次，那么无论怎么分组，它能贡献的分数最大为$\lfloor S / K \rfloor$，因此可以得到上面的结论。</p><p>于是最后问题就转化为了求出所以前缀出现次数的问题。对于第一个点，由于字符串长度较小，直接map就可以。当字符串长度很大时，存下来所有的前缀就会爆内存，此时使用trie树存储就好。</p><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> <span class="built_in">std</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> ans, N, K;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">trie</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> cnt = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    trie *son[<span class="number">26</span>] = &#123;<span class="literal">nullptr</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">insert</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="built_in">string</span>&amp; s, <span class="keyword">int</span> now)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (s.length() == now) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> idx = s[now] - <span class="string">'A'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!son[idx]) son[idx] = <span class="keyword">new</span> trie();</span><br><span class="line">        son[idx]-&gt;cnt += <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        son[idx]-&gt;insert(s, now + <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Sum</span><span class="params">(trie* r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (r-&gt;cnt &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) ans += r-&gt;cnt / K;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; item : r-&gt;son) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!item) <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        Sum(item);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ios::sync_with_stdio(<span class="literal">false</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> T;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; T;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">string</span> s;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; T; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        trie root&#123;&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; N &gt;&gt; K;</span><br><span class="line">        ans = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; N; ++j) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; s;</span><br><span class="line">            root.insert(s, <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        Sum(&amp;root);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">"Case #"</span> &lt;&lt; i + <span class="number">1</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">": "</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="体验"><a href="#体验" class="headerlink" title="体验"></a>体验</h2><p>Kick Start的题目还是挺有意思的（对于我这种菜鸡来说），尤其是最后一道题，能想到性质的话实现起来非常容易了，这个性质还是很神奇。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>kick start 2020 round A第三题</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/25/kick-start-2020-round-A%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E9%A2%98/"/>
      <url>/2020/03/25/kick-start-2020-round-A%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E9%A2%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这道题目实际上不难，然而毕竟自己第一次打kick start，也好久不碰算法题了。在这里记录一下</p><h2 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h2><p>具体原文背景就不再翻译了，题目大意是：给定一组严格递增的数据，可以在其中插入数据，同时要保证数列仍然是严格递增的，最多插入$K$个新数据。问最终的最大间隔最小值是多少。</p><p>输入数据格式：T表示测试数据组数，紧接着每一组数据先输入$N$，$K$表示初始有$N$个数据，最多能插入$K$个。接下来输出N个初始数据$X_i$。</p><p>输出：最大间隔的最小值。</p><h2 id="题解"><a href="#题解" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h2><p>第一个点仅仅要求$K=1$，这是很容易的，因为此时唯一一种选择就是将最大区间对半分。然而如果顺着这个思路往下走，就会<del>像我一样</del>误入歧途了。因为当$K&gt;1$的时候，显然一直对半分是不正确的。例如初始数据是$1, 13$且$K=2$，那么对半分两次得到的结果是6，不如三等分。因此要决定每个区间分多少份是一件不太好做的事情，而我一直在想这个东西能不能dp……就失败了。</p><p>正确的做法是二分（似乎当你不知道怎么办的时候二分就对了.jpg）。假设初始所有间隔为$d_1, d_2, …d_{N-1}$，那么如果想要得到一个结果为$ans$的分割方式，那么对每个$d_i$至少要切$\lceil \frac{d_i}{ans} \rceil + 1$次，将其加起来如果不大于$K$，那么说明$ans$是可行的，否则是不可行的。因此对$ans$进行二分即可找出答案。</p><p>代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> <span class="built_in">std</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; sessions;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">judge</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> K, <span class="keyword">int</span> tmp)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> Sum = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> item : sessions) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (item % tmp == <span class="number">0</span>) Sum += item / tmp - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> Sum += item / tmp;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> Sum &lt;= K;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> T;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; T;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; T; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        sessions.<span class="built_in">clear</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> N, K;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; N &gt;&gt; K;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> x = <span class="number">0</span>, lastx = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> m = <span class="number">0</span>, M = <span class="number">1e9</span> + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> ans = (m + M) / <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; N; ++j) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; x;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (j &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                sessions.push_back(x - lastx);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            lastx = x;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="literal">true</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">bool</span> flag = judge(K, ans);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (flag) M = ans;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> m = ans;</span><br><span class="line">            ans = (m + M) / <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (M - m == <span class="number">1</span>) <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        ans = M;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">"Case #"</span> &lt;&lt; i + <span class="number">1</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">": "</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> 算法题目 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Ubuntu安装Windows10双系统</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/10/ubuntu_install_win10/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/10/ubuntu_install_win10/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>因为在学校的时候有台式机装着Win10作为主力机，作为日常工作<del>（打游戏）</del>用，自己的笔记本SSD又小，因此就把自己的笔记本上Win10卸载了，装了Ubuntu作为笔记本的主力系统。然而回到家之后因为万恶的病毒被困在了家里，Ubuntu不支持网课软件，不得已又需要把Windows装回来。Win装Ubuntu双系统的教程一抓一大把了，反向装回去做法也差不多，无非就是做启动盘=&gt;插入=&gt;安装。这里姑且记录一下遇到的几个小问题。</p><h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><p>第一步当然是下载ISO镜像，然后烧制启动盘。</p><p>Ubuntu上做个启动盘没windows上那么方便，<code>dd</code>命令我也不是很熟悉，一开始先尝试了<code>mkfs.vfat /dev/sdc</code>格式化U盘之后再通过<code>dd</code>命令进行写入，但是莫名其妙卡死了。然后我就去找第三方工具了2333。</p><blockquote><p>不要重复造轮子  –鲁迅</p></blockquote><p>Ubuntu上找到了一个叫<code>woeusb</code>的软件，实际上就是给几个Linux命令提供了图形化界面的参数设置（总之对于我这种不大熟悉shell命令的菜鸡来说舒服多了）。用法和win上的UltraISO差不多。但是在最终刻写完成之后，你应该会发现它报了一个error，这个error实在过于奇妙，它是因为在最后清理垃圾的一个命令因为linux内核更新有一个参数不支持了（它的github上一次commit还是在几个月之前）……但是好在这并不影响启动盘的烧制，这时候启动盘已经做好了，只不过收尾工作似乎出了点问题，github上的issue里大家最后也没讨论出来结果那个报错的一句话到底干了啥……</p><p>所以到这里为止我们的启动盘就做完了！</p><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><p>安装的时候要注意自己的磁盘是GPT分区还是MBR分区，如果是GPT分区的话要在主板设置上打开UEFI启动，通过UEFI启动做好的系统盘。在这个时候我还报了一个小问题就是“Windows检测到EFI系统分区格式化为NTFS”。网上查的好多结果说是GPT分区没设好，然而我又确认了一下我的确是GPT分区+UEFI启动。只得又回到Ubuntu查看一下磁盘状态。Ubuntu18.04自带一个软件叫<code>disks</code>，简直是shell手残党的福音（<code>fdisk</code>相关命令看得我头大）。发现是上次卸载windows的时候它的EFI分区我并没有除掉，把这个分区搞掉，就完事大吉辣！</p><p>（不得不说，即使在机械盘上启动需要两分钟的卡顿windows10也比Ubuntu的桌面来得香，我终于能玩Overwatch啦！！！）</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> 装系统记录 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
